high_descs: Go to the glass coffee table.
Pick up the credit card off of the table.
Turn towards the TV and face the first white chair on the right.
Place the credit card on the chair.
Walk over to the dining room table.
Pick up the credit card off of the table.
Return to the white chair.
Place the credit card next to the first on the chair.
anns.task_desc: Place two credit cards on the white chair in the living room.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the table in the middle of the other room.
Grab the credit card from the table.
Turn right then right again to face the chairs.
Place the credit card on the chair on the right.
Turn right then left to go to the first room, then take a left then a right to face the table.
Grab the credit card from the table.
Turn right and walk back to the room with the two chairs.
Place the second credit card to the right of the first one.
anns.task_desc: Place two credit cards on the chair

high_descs: Turn around and walk two steps, turn left for three steps, turn right and walk to the coffee table and stop.
Pick up the credit card in front of the remote on the coffee table.
Turn right for three steps, turn left for one step, turn right for two steps and turn right to face the chairs.
Put the credit card on the bottom left side of the cushion on the chair to the right.
Turn right and take five steps, turn left and take seven steps, turn left for three steps, turn right for six steps then turn right to face the table.
Pick up the credit card on the table between the two chairs.
Turn right for six steps, turn left for three steps, turn right for seven steps, turn right for three steps, turn left for one, turn right for one step, turn right to face the chairs.
Put the credit to the right of the first credit card on the cushion, with their ends touching slightly.
anns.task_desc: Put two credits cards on the cushion of a chair.
